# Day 3 - NumPy Basics

##  Objective
Learn the fundamentals of NumPy and how it is used for numerical computations in Python.

---

##  What I Practiced

- Created 1D NumPy arrays
- Performed basic operations on arrays
- Created 2D NumPy arrays`
 

---

## 📈 What I Learned

- NumPy is faster and more efficient than Python lists for numerical data  
- Arrays are relative objects.  
- Useful for data science and machine learning  
